1031
01:26:20,100 --> 01:26:22,100
and adding cool features to it.

1032
01:26:22,100 --> 01:26:24,100
So we said, why don't we use this?

1033
01:26:24,100 --> 01:26:28,100
Because basically, a game engine is a world simulator.

1034
01:26:28,100 --> 01:26:30,100
Let's try that.

1035
01:26:30,100 --> 01:26:36,100
And after a while, we found even though theoretically they're the same,

1036
01:26:36,100 --> 01:26:40,100
there's some really fundamental differences between a game engine

1037
01:26:40,100 --> 01:26:45,100
